TITLE: Using the useBottomTabBarHeight Hook for Layout Adjustments
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the useBottomTabBarHeight hook to get the height of the bottom tab bar, which is useful for positioning components relative to the tab bar.
SOURCE: https://github.com/callstackincubator/react-native-bottom-tabs/blob/main/docs/docs/docs/guides/usage-with-react-navigation.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
